    "description": "A completely synthetic triarylmethane dye manufactured from petroleum-derived chemicals through sulfonation of aromatic amine intermediates. Not found in nature. Produces bright green colour in solution. One of the most controversial green food dyes - banned in more countries than it is approved in."
